	abstract = {We have performed two-dimensional multicomponent decomposition of 144 
local barred spiral galaxies using 3.6 $\mu$m images from the Spitzer
Survey of Stellar Structure in Galaxies. Our model fit includes up to
four components (bulge, disk, bar, and a point source) and, most
